### Phase 3: Authentication Overhaul

---

#### [NEW] [AuthProvider.jsx](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderBlock/client/src/context/AuthProvider.jsx)

New context that wraps FlowProvider:
- Tracks: `walletAddress`, `isWalletConnected`, `isAdmin`, `authMethod` (wallet/jwt/none)
- Checks admin status: compares wallet address to known admin address (`0xea0627a8b29d7901`)
- Provides `connectWallet()`, `disconnectWallet()`, `isAuthenticated()`

---

#### [MODIFY] [App.jsx](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderBlock/client/src/App.jsx)

Wrap routes with `AuthProvider`

---

#### [MODIFY] [Bids.jsx](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderBlock/client/src/containers/bids/Bids.jsx)

- Require wallet connection to place bids (show "Connect Wallet" if not connected)
- Display wallet address as bidder identity

---

#### [MODIFY] [Login.jsx](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderBlock/client/src/containers/login/Login.jsx)

Add deprecation banner: "We recommend using wallet-based login for full blockchain features." Add "Connect Wallet" button alongside existing login form.

---

#### [MODIFY] [Signup.jsx](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderBlock/client/src/containers/signup/Signup.jsx)

Add deprecation banner: "We recommend using wallet-based signup for full blockchain features." Add "Connect Wallet" button alongside existing signup form.

